       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI10204         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD7601 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD7001 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01 WS-SQL-AUXILIARY.
         05 IND-NULL                       PIC S9(04) BINARY.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV1020.
       COPY COCV1021.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0010.
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.
       COPY TGCL2000.
       COPY EXCL0200.
       COPY ETCL0002.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT7601 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT7601'.
           05 CON-COVT7001 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT7001'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CPAIS  PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR047'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-LNEG   PIC X(05) VALUE 'CO702'.
           05 CON-MANUAL   PIC X(06) VALUE 'MANUAL'.
           05 CON-IN       PIC X(02) VALUE 'IN'.
           05 CON-AP       PIC X(02) VALUE 'AP'.
           05 CON-01       PIC X(02) VALUE '01'.
           05 CON-8        PIC 9(01) VALUE 8.
           05 CON-SEP      PIC X(01) VALUE '-'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME     PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI10204'.
           05 WS-NIDPROJECTO       PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-NHORAS            PIC 9(03) VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-TOTAL             PIC 9(08) VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-TOTALHORAS        PIC 9(08) VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-TOTALHORAS-FERIAS PIC 9(08) VALUE ZEROS.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI10204         '.
