       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV1020-MSG.
           MOVE COCV1020-ASE               TO COCV1021-ASE.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV1020-ADE               TO COCV1021-ADE.

           PERFORM 2100-VALIDACOES
              THRU 2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT

      *--- Apaga registos que năo estejam aprovados
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
               PERFORM 2140-APAGA-DADOS
                  THRU 2140-APAGA-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Insere Ausęncias (se com dados)
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV1020-NIDPROJECTO1 NOT = SPACES
           AND COCV1020-CSITU1       NOT = CON-AP
               MOVE COCV1020-NIDPROJECTO1 TO WS-NIDPROJECTO
               MOVE COCV1020-NHORAS1      TO WS-NHORAS
               PERFORM 2150-INSERE-DADOS
                  THRU 2150-INSERE-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV1020-NIDPROJECTO2 NOT = SPACES
           AND COCV1020-CSITU2       NOT = CON-AP
               MOVE COCV1020-NIDPROJECTO2 TO WS-NIDPROJECTO
               MOVE COCV1020-NHORAS2      TO WS-NHORAS
               PERFORM 2150-INSERE-DADOS
                  THRU 2150-INSERE-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV1020-NIDPROJECTO3 NOT = SPACES
           AND COCV1020-CSITU3       NOT = CON-AP
               MOVE COCV1020-NIDPROJECTO3 TO WS-NIDPROJECTO
               MOVE COCV1020-NHORAS3      TO WS-NHORAS
